body:
Hey guys! I'm back with another "Player of the Week". First off, I would like to apologize for this being put up late. Here's a reminder of the rules!
        Here's how it works:
In this thread, you will be able to nominate up to 3 different players, and yes, you may nominate yourself. You may nominate staff but it defeats the purpose of the topic. You may also ask people to nominate you. 
The three players who have the most nominations will then be put into a voting system where you can vote for your favorite. Keep in mind, You may only vote once.
After the voting period is over, I will contact the player via skype or teamspeak. 
*Note: The player must be active on the forums, or you must provide me with their skype in order for me to contact them.
Special Thanks to- RCMP_Mountie & Sulorak for offering to help me manage this topic.

Nominations Close after 48 hours. Be sure to check back for the final voting round and vote for who you think deserves "Player of the Week"! ^.^You may start nominating below, have fun :D
